            "title": "盤中速報 - 科派特(CPRT-US)大跌5.01%，報57.62美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>科派特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CPRT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CPRT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CPRT-US</a>)截至台北時間23日21:30股價下跌3.04美元，報57.62美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量163,930（股），盤中最高價58.07美元、最低價57.44美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.89%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.93%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.58%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-2.4%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>科派特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CPRT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CPRT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CPRT-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.67%</li> <li>近 1 月：+0.41%</li> <li>近 3 月：+7.19%</li> <li>近 6 月：-3.25%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.7%</li></ul></section></main>",
