            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)截至台北時間23日21:30股價上漲53.93美元，報720.00美元，漲幅8.1%，成交量261,282（股），盤中最高價721.24美元、最低價717.42美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.87%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.93%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.59%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-2.44%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>直覺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTU-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.72%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.14%</li> <li>近 3 月：+17.79%</li> <li>近 6 月：+4.05%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.98%</li></ul></section></main>",
